@startuml StateDiagram
[*] --> Instantiated
Instantiated --> ConfigurationLoaded : Config dict assigned
ConfigurationLoaded --> ExecutingPipeline : run() triggered
state ExecutingPipeline {
  [*] --> IngestingFrames
  IngestingFrames --> ModelingGraphs : Apply ML algorithms
  ModelingGraphs --> BuildingArtifacts : Populate structures
}
ExecutingPipeline --> CompletedSuccessfully : Computation completed
ExecutingPipeline --> ExecutionFailed : Exception raised
CompletedSuccessfully --> FileWritten : save_interactive_plot()
FileWritten --> [*]
ExecutionFailed --> [*]
@endum